      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="a12b1bd2019c3f30" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: A dragon can bite one target or claw two opponents in immediate range as a single action. When bitten, targets are also immobilized until they succeed on a Might defense roll to break free (or the dragon drops them).</source>
