      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="a4ee135ae0463694" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Most dragons have one or more additional magical abilities they can bring to bear in combat, including the following.</source>
        <target></target>
        <context-group name="" purpose="location">
